by the western garden.

854
00:39:23,190 --> 00:39:26,060
Why is Your Highness
inquiring about Young Lord Zhang?

855
00:39:26,060 --> 00:39:27,190
If he's here,

856
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:28,350
Uncle and Aunt

857
00:39:28,350 --> 00:39:29,190
won't have to worry about

858
00:39:29,190 --> 00:39:30,710
Minmin's marriage anymore.

859
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,630
What if he hasn't come?

860
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:35,100
If he doesn't show up,

861
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:37,020
it would still be good for Minmin

862
00:39:37,020 --> 00:39:38,820
to get to know Young Master Zhou.

863
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:40,440
But I believe

864
00:39:40,870 --> 00:39:43,380
Young Lord Zhang must have already
heard the news

865
00:39:43,380 --> 00:39:45,530
and arrived early to prepare.

866
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:46,870
Yes.

867
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:04,450
Princess, are you alright?

868
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:07,870
I suddenly feel a sharp pain

869
00:40:07,870 --> 00:40:08,980
in my abdomen.

870
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:11,230
Madam,

871
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,350
maybe we should reschedule the matchmaking.

872
00:40:13,350 --> 00:40:14,310
Yes, Madam.

873
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:15,420
Princess,

874
00:40:15,830 --> 00:40:17,980
your little tricks

875
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,540
won't fool me.

876
00:40:19,540 --> 00:40:21,020
I...

877
00:40:23,670 --> 00:40:24,700
Princess,

878
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:26,550
the Empress Dowager

879
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:28,830
has worn herself out
worrying about the Su family.

880
00:40:28,830 --> 00:40:31,550
You should try to be more understanding.

881
00:40:32,790 --> 00:40:34,790
Your engagement to Young Master Gao

882
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:36,900
is also part of her thoughtful plan,

883
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,630
all for the sake of your future.

884
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:39,920
No matter

885
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:41,540
how idle Gao Chen may seem now,

886
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:43,470
one day, he will inherit the title.

887
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,700
When that time comes,

888
00:40:45,750 --> 00:40:47,750
you'll be a marquise,

889
00:40:47,980 --> 00:40:49,440
with the whole marquisate

890
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:51,360
under your command.

891
00:40:51,910 --> 00:40:53,000
Madam is keeping a close eye.

892
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,730
I really couldn't do anything.

893
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:00,800
Well, since things have come to this,

894
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:02,330
I'll go then.

895
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:13,560
What is she doing here?

896
00:41:24,750 --> 00:41:25,740
Madam,

897
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:28,310
I was thoughtless before

898
00:41:28,580 --> 00:41:31,060
and didn't appreciate Grandmother's efforts.

899
00:41:31,060 --> 00:41:32,440
But what you just said

900
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:33,710
has enlightened me.

901
00:41:34,380 --> 00:41:35,430
Since I'm already here,

902
00:41:35,430 --> 00:41:37,160
there's no harm in meeting him.

903
00:41:38,270 --> 00:41:40,310
I'm glad you've come around, Princess.

904
00:41:40,310 --> 00:41:42,100
Young Master Gao will be here shortly.

905
00:41:42,100 --> 00:41:44,380
Let me accompany you
to the side room while we wait.

906
00:41:44,380 --> 00:41:45,020
Let's go.

907
00:41:47,020 --> 00:41:48,980
When it comes to matchmaking,

908
00:41:49,150 --> 00:41:51,150
men and women should speak

909
00:41:51,230 --> 00:41:52,890
freely and honestly.

910
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,020
Only then can they

911
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:55,640
truly get to know each other.

912
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:57,290
If you're present,

913
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,250
Young Master Gao might be
too formal and hold back.

914
00:42:00,420 --> 00:42:02,230
He won't show his true self.

915
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:05,230
Why don't you wait outside, Nanny?

916
00:42:05,230 --> 00:42:06,630
I'll meet with him alone.

917
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:10,650
Madam,

918
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:12,620
I'm already here.

919
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:14,570
It's not like I can just run off now.

920
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:16,090
Besides,

921
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:17,400
whether I go through
with the matchmaking or not,

922
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:19,040
Grandmother will find out either way.

923
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:20,440
Why would I lie to you?

924
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:25,650
Take your time, Princess.

925
00:42:25,750 --> 00:42:28,270
Have a proper conversation
with Young Master Gao

926
00:42:28,270 --> 00:42:30,400
and get to know him better.

927
00:42:30,430 --> 00:42:31,100
Alright, Madam.

928
00:42:31,100 --> 00:42:31,950
Don't worry.

929
00:43:09,020 --> 00:43:10,790
He can't even be punctual for a matchmaking.

930
00:43:10,790 --> 00:43:13,710
What value is there
in all his so-called talent and virtue?

931
00:43:13,710 --> 00:43:14,980
Nanzhi, let's go.

932
00:43:19,210 --> 00:43:20,150
Miss Bai.

933
00:43:22,500 --> 00:43:23,310
Miss Bai,

934
00:43:23,460 --> 00:43:24,980
I apologize for being late.

935
00:43:24,980 --> 00:43:26,460
I was teaching my younger brother
the Nine Arithmetical Operations,

936
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:27,590
part of the Six Arts.

937
00:43:27,630 --> 00:43:29,380
I got so engrossed
that I lost track of time.

938
00:43:29,380 --> 00:43:30,530
It was truly thoughtless of me.

939
00:43:30,530 --> 00:43:32,130
Please forgive me, Miss Bai.

940
00:43:32,790 --> 00:43:35,470
What are the Six Arts
and the Nine Arithmetical Operations?

941
00:43:35,470 --> 00:43:36,610
To instill proper conduct
in the youth of our nation,

942
00:43:36,610 --> 00:43:38,070
we teach them the Six Arts.

943
00:43:38,270 --> 00:43:39,530
First: the Five Rites.

944
00:43:39,540 --> 00:43:40,940
Second: the Six Forms of Music.

945
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:41,960
Third: the Five Techniques of Archery.

946
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:42,730
Fourth: the Five Techniques of Horsemanship.

947
00:43:42,730 --> 00:43:43,640
Fifth: the Six Styles of Calligraphy.

948
00:43:43,640 --> 00:43:44,530
And sixth: the Nine Arithmetical Operations.

949
00:43:44,530 --> 00:43:45,640
The Nine Arithmetical Operations include:

950
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:46,730
measuring farmland, converting grain ratios,

951
00:43:46,730 --> 00:43:47,780
calculating tax distribution,
measuring land dimensions...

952
00:43:47,780 --> 00:43:48,500
Young Master Zhou.

953
00:43:48,500 --> 00:43:49,710
Estimating earthworks,
calculating transport costs,

954
00:43:49,710 --> 00:43:50,540
solving equations,
computing gains and losses...

955
00:43:50,540 --> 00:43:51,390
Young Master Zhou!
